-- LDK Solar Agrees $8.9 Billion Loan From China Development Bank
-- B y   B e n   S i l l s
-- 2010-09-27T07:23:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-27/ldk-solar-agrees-to-a-8-9-billion-loan-from-china-development-bank-corp-.html
LDK Solar Co. Ltd, a Chinese
photovoltaic wafer maker, agreed a 60 billion yuan ($8.9
billion), five-year loan from China Development Bank Corporation
to fund its expansion plans, the company said in a filing.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Sills at 
 bsills@bloomberg.net  